  <name>drI18nRoutingExtractPlugin</name>
  <channel>pear.symfony-project.com</channel>
  <summary>Provides a task for extracting translatable strings from the routing</summary>
  <description>This plugin provides a task called i18n:extract-routing, which parses all the routes from your application, extracts all translatable strings and places them in a messages catalogue file, that can be read by the culture-aware routing system provided by the zxI18nRoutingPlugin</description>
